"\n"
"Utarejeshwa kiotomatiki katika tarehe hiyo. Ikiwa una maswali, tafadhali "
"wasiliana na msimamizi wa tovuti.\n"
"\n"
"— %2$s"

#. translators: 1: artist display name, 2: site name
