msgstr "Uanachama wako katika %s umesitishwa"

#. translators: 1: artist display name, 2: site name
#: includes/Artist/DepartureNotification.php:276
#, php-format
msgid ""
"Hi %1$s,\n"
"\n"
"Your temporary suspension at %2$s has ended and your membership has been "
"reinstated. You can now log in and submit work as before.\n"
"\n"
"— %2$s"
msgstr ""
"Habari %1$s,\n"
"\n"
"Kusimamishwa kwako kwa muda katika %2$s kumekwisha na uanachama wako "
"umerejeshwa. Sasa unaweza kuingia na kuwasilisha kazi kama hapo awali.\n"
"\n"
"— %2$s"

#. translators: %s: site name
#: includes/Artist/DepartureNotification.php:298
#, php-format
msgid "Your membership at %s has been reinstated"
msgstr "Uanachama wako katika %s umerejeshwa"

#. translators: 1: voter display name, 2: site name, 3: closing date, 4: yes URL, 5: no URL
#: includes/Artist/DepartureNotification.php:360
#, php-format
msgid ""
"Hi %1$s,\n"
"\n"
"The %2$s community has opened a vote to remove a member. The vote closes on "
"%3$s.\n"
"\n"
"Cast your vote:\n"
"\n"
"Vote YES (remove): %4$s\n"
"\n"
"Vote NO (keep):    %5$s\n"
"\n"
"A majority of active members (more than 50%%) must vote yes for the removal "
"to proceed. You can change your vote by clicking the other link before the "
"deadline.\n"
"\n"
"— %2$s"
msgstr ""
"Habari %1$s,\n"
"\n"
"Jumuiya ya %2$s imefungua kura ya kumwondoa mwanachama. Kura itafungwa "
"tarehe %3$s.\n"
"\n"
"Piga kura yako:\n"
"\n"
"Piga kura NDIO (ondoa): %4$s\n"
"\n"
"Piga kura HAPANA (salia):    %5$s\n"
"\n"
"Wengi wa wanachama hai (zaidi ya 50%%) lazima wapige kura ya ndiyo ili "
"kuondolewa kuendelee. Unaweza kubadilisha kura yako kwa kubofya kiungo "
"kingine kabla ya muda wa mwisho.\n"
"\n"
"— %2$s"

