#: blocks/newsletter-popover/block.json
msgctxt "block description"
msgid ""
"Icon button that opens a full-viewport popover containing the newsletter "
"signup form. Self-contained — drop it directly into a header or footer "
"template part; renders nothing when the public newsletter is disabled "
"(Settings → Newsletter)."
msgstr ""
"Kitufe cha ikoni kinachofungua dirisha ibukizi linalochukua skrini nzima "
"lenye fomu ya kujisajili kwa jarida la barua. Kinafanya kazi kivyake — "
"kiweke moja kwa moja kwenye kiolezo cha kichwa au chini ya ukurasa; "
"hakionyeshi chochote wakati jarida la umma limezimwa (Mipangilio → Jarida la "
"Barua)."

